casebody.data:
(March 9, 1955.)

(Republished.)

418 Trading Corp., Respondent, v. Moon Realty Corp. et al., Appellants, et al., Defendants.

Order granting plaintiff-respondent’s motion for summary judgment of foreclosure reversed and motion denied; order denying defendants-appellants’ cross motion for summary judgment modified so as to dismiss the complaint with leave to serve an amended complaint; order denying defendants-appellants’ motion for reargument dismissed. Opinion Per Curiam. All concur. Present — Cohn, J. P., Callahan, Breitel, Botein and Rabin, JJ. [See ante, p. 444.]
